{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["Shiranui, the Do-It-All Shopkeeper\n\n<size=45>Chapter 3: The Shopkeeper's Little Buddies<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"Port - Supply Shop","dir":1,"bgm":"story-1","side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"On this day off, I once again concealed myself next to the shop, quietly observing the situation.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Please,  Shiranui, just think about the deep bond we used to share, and let me interview you!","actor":303030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"I don't remember ever doing anything with you that would resemble a \"deep bond.\"","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":301180},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Unapproachable and mysterious, the ghostly owner of the Supply Shop- this interview is gonna sell like hotcakes!","actor":303030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"If you used your segment to promote my shop, I might consider it.","actor":301180,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"No problem! Let's get started right away!","dir":1,"side":0,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0.2,"dur":0.2,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":303030},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"First and foremost, those disheveled animal ears on your head! Is it true that the ghosts make you wear them like that?","actor":303030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"... I bumped them a few times while organizing things. I thought it'd be a waste to replace them, so I didn't bother getting them fixed.","actor":301180,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Uhh... the rumor that you're actually a ghost... Is it true?","actor":303030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Are you an idiot?","actor":301180,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"What about that will-o'-wisp circling you?!","actor":303030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"That's just a floating prop that I got from Akashi because it looked cool.","actor":301180,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Th-then... the rumor that you can see ghosts as well...?","dir":1,"side":0,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":3,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":303030},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"I suppose that does happen every now and then.","actor":301180,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Ah, so that's also a fabrica-","actor":303030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Ehhh??? It's true?!","dir":1,"side":0,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.1,"number":3,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":303030},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"It's true. For example, there's one crawling up your back right now...","actor":301180,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Waaaaaaaaaaaaahhhh!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.1,"number":3,"x":0},{"type":"move","y":0,"delay":0.6,"dur":0.3,"x":-1800}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":303030},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Of course, that's just a lie...","actor":301180,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"However, our very existence already defies the laws of science. It shouldn't be strange at all to see strange things.","actor":301180,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Today, I feel like I learned a bit more about another side of Shiranui.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"However, I feel like she just shot a glance over here. It's just my imagination... right?","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"BUZHIHUO3","fadeOut":1.5}